Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  今天也要精精神神地去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天會返還試卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼  肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不休息可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要管我了你們先走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試成績要給我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算今天休息考試成績也不會變  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出門嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:17.35,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,300)}春天的開始、南家的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:25.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還是那麼充滿人情味的絕妙分數
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能不會令春香滿意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回考試不扭轉現狀就不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  找人教我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我功課
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  夏奈不會認真學的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了我這認真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  現在沒戴眼鏡看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好奇怪  剛才還戴著的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:05:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子沒有回應我的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.06,0:05:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  去海邊吧去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求別人的時候  比起認真來純真才更重要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪  美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高和我家的千秋差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  純樸的眼神很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這麼說雖然很失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成績不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼突然也太失禮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個讓你提高成績的好提議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  教美雪功課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我家教就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雪這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好很棒喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我看上的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  這裏教我下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己稍微動動腦筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  這裏教我下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:28.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼光偏袒美雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.33,0:06:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了教美雪的功課才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  不要那麼生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.07,0:06:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過拜託別人得到想要的只適用於小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠自己的力量去達成目的這才是學習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.21,0:06:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如夏奈所說的我要靠自己的力量努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個氣勢  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  降了一分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然光靠一個人的力量是不行的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類不互相幫助是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了夏奈  我第一次得了100分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去做就能成功的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我長高的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以  不過要教我功課
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.48,0:07:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類要互相幫助才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  教我功課
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
